title: A Woman Unhinged
itunes:title: A Woman Unhinged
description: Jackie is back from Australia, jet-lagged and bitchier than ever. She recounts her unlucky flying history, Real Housewives and why Bermuda shorts are for people who have never been to Bermuda.
